title: SimplePlanes (GOG)
description:
Install instructions:
- Run "setup_simpleplanes_2.0.0.2.exe"
- Play
PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS! :)
If you like this game, support the developers and BUY IT!

Title: SIMPLEPLANES
Genre: Simulation - Building - Sandbox
Works on: Windows (Vista, 7, 8, 10) and Mac OS X (10.9+)
Languages: Audio and text: English
Features: single-player - achievements - controller support
Released: December 17, 2015
Size: 214.3 MB
Company: Jundroo, LLC / Jundroo, LLC
Rating:	ESRB Rating: Everyone
Store page: https://www.gog.com/game/simpleplanes

About:
Build airplanes by snapping parts together, designing wing sections, and attaching engines. At any time, you can strap yourself into the cockpit and see how it flies with realistic physics. If you're not in the mood for building, over 100,000 airplanes are available to download for free.
Build airplanes with an easy to use designer by snapping parts together.
Over 100,000 airplanes available to downloaded for free from SimplePlanes.com.
Tons of parts to choose from. Build everything from airplanes to cars to boats, all with realistic physics.

Minimum system requirements - Windows: Vista / 7 / 8 / 10
Processor: Core 2 Duo
Memory: 2GB RAM
Graphics: SM3 512MB VRAM
Storage: 750MB
Mouse, Keyboard

Recommended system requirements - Windows: 7 / 8 / 10
Processor: Core i5
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: SM4 1GB VRAM
Storage: 1 GB available space
